name: Death and Other Details
overview: How do you solve a murder in a post-fact world? Especially when sailing the Mediterranean on an ocean liner filled with the wealthy and powerful. Everyone on board is hiding something… but is one of them a killer? That’s what the world’s once greatest detective, Rufus Cotesworth, and his protégée, Imogene, aim to discover.

episodes.name: Rare
episodes.overview: When a guest is murdered on a luxury ocean liner, Imogene Scott becomes the only suspect in an impossible crime. She didn't do it. So, who did?

episodes.name: Sordid
episodes.overview: Rufus interrogates each of the major players on board. They're all hiding something… even Imogene's best friend.

episodes.name: Troublesome
episodes.overview: Interpol seizes control of the investigation. Rufus and Imogene must now investigate the Colliers in secret.

episodes.name: Hidden
episodes.overview: As the manhunt for Jules intensifies, Imogene uncovers his criminal past… and finds a new witness.

episodes.name: Exquisite
episodes.overview: Who is Viktor Sams? Imogene and Sunil pursue a lead in Malta, while Rufus teams up with Leila and Teddy.

episodes.name: Tragic
episodes.overview: Imogene is betrayed by someone close to her as more victims fall prey to Viktor Sams.

episodes.name: Memorable
episodes.overview: Imogene walks in Rufus's shoes, revisiting the investigation into her mother’s murder eighteen years ago.

episodes.name: Vanishing
episodes.overview: Blackout. Three dead bodies. Everyone's terrified. The secrets unravel like Christmas presents. And Imogene confronts her mother's killer.

episodes.name: Impossible
episodes.overview: Viktor Sams takes control of the Varuna and forces the guests to bid against each other to survive. Will Imogene and her friends unmask him before time runs out?

episodes.name: Chilling
episodes.overview: Reeling from the truth, Imogene has a choice to make. Rufus writes a second memoir.
